@node intro "Introduction"

 What is it for?

       Move tagged files to fidonet poll. This is very useful for points.
       ATTENTION! You need KickStart 2.04 or higher.

@endnode

@node using "Using"

   Add this for your FileMenu:


   [ 1] Letter:                   W                                  
   [ 2] Executable: (path/name)   Dlg:DiaBTag                        
   [ 4] Description:              TagAttach                          
   [ 5] Type:                     Executable                         
   [10] Load type:                OVERLAY                            
   [12] Pend messages:            NO                                 
   [13] Cli mode:                 YES                                
   [14] Pause on completion:      NO                                 
   [16] Activity string:          Moving Tagged Files To FidoNet Poll

@endnode

@node display "Display"

                            ---

