@node history "History"

 
       V1.0 - The first version.
              05/11/92
  
       V1.1 - Optimized and fixed release.
              (Stardate 7112.5.9)

              o Now support only KS2.04+ machines.
              o Code optimized.
              o Support now CTRL+C.
              o Use Amigaguide format (Docs).
              o Using now dlg.library.
              o Add GetDevName routine (%UName no more needed).    

@endnode

